Hayley Sandiford must get rid of her American bulldog Winston by the end of April or she will lose her house in Blackburn . 
  The pet has attacked several postmen and has 'a thing' for chewing up mail . 
  Post has been banned from 60 homes in the area since February 2014 . 
  But housing association has now ordered her to leave her home this month . 
  She says Royal Mail are victimising her and has been 'taunted'